## Recurring Interview Themes

```dataview
TABLE WITHOUT ID
  count(key_themes) as "Count",
  key_themes as "Theme"
FROM "Athlete Financial Empowerment/02-interviews"
WHERE contains(file.tags, "#interview") AND key_themes
FLATTEN key_themes
GROUP BY key_themes
SORT count(key_themes) desc
```